name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Map for real estate listing websites

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds map to real estate listing website for easier navigation in offers

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Improves experience of using real estate listing websites by adding a map to the listing page to see locations of all items listed on the current page.
Currently supports:
- nehnutelnosti.sk

Contribute: https://github.com/witcher-development/flat-search-with-map
